# Machine-local handoffs. Ignored by default so a stray commit — or a
# branchStrategy:head Sandcastle container that has none of a local
# .git/info/exclude — can never accidentally publish one to this PUBLIC repo.
# To share a handoff cross-machine, `git add -f` it deliberately, and treat it
# as public (no secrets, no work-account/employer references). See CLAUDE.md.
